    "summary": "Jimena is a Global Recruiter and Talent Manager with more than 15 years experience in all Industries (Financial, Energy, Engineering, Information Technology, Pharma, Consumer goods, etc.), assessing and hiring top executives, which match company needs and culture. She combines best practices from the leading executive search companies with tailor-made solutions for her clients. \n\nPreviously, she worked at Kornferry, the leading executive search company with presence in 40 countries. She partners with companies to improve organizational health and effectiveness, which leads to better results, over both the short and long term. Previously she has worked with Great Places To Work in order to help companies understand how they can build effective environments to grow and retain the best talent.\n\nJimena has a PhD on Demography and a first class Bachelors degree in Sociology and Political Sciences, she completed her post graduate studies in Heidelberg, Germany. In her academic, social and political background, she has more than ten years experience in the field of Human Rights, labour rights, development, social justice and public policy in the European Union, Americas, Africa, Asia and Oceania. \n\nJimena is Spanish and speaks also excellent English and German, good French and intermediate Dutch. She is currently preparing her NT2 Exams (Dutch as a second language)",
