                    "company": "Jimena Puy",
                    "description": "Global Recruiter with more than 15 years experience at the top level in all industries, assessing and hiring top executives, which match company needs and culture; combining the best practices learnt and developed in the best leading executive search companies, with tailor made solutions for my clients.\n\nAs Talent Manager,  I guide professionals in their career paths to develop the best of themselves designing a talent development strategy that both, maximises their potential and gives their best to their companies and organizations. I achieve this using one-to-one and also teaching groups, both face-to-face and remote, as part of ongoing coaching and mentoring, which is often integrated into performance management processes. \n\nUtilising the leaders of teams, working hand-in-hand with the HR Business Partners, I create and implement  effective, dynamic, and transparent mechanisms in the form of leadership programmes and post learning coaching and opportunities, which can be integrated and embedded into talent selection, performance and succession management, progression, and the annual talent review cycle. I work with large companies in an international setting working together with institutional stakeholders.\n\nI also help Organizations and companies to define the structures of the teams and constituent positions and I link this to the talent development plans including Talent acquisition and management. \n\nI develop training courses that meet the companies needs and teaches the leaders how to personally guide and coach their teams after acquiring the theory in a formal setting, as it has been proven that this direct coaching is by far the most effective way of development. This includes leadership training and technical development specifically focused on how to apply techniques in their current role to get the most from the investment both financial and time wise.",
                    "title": "Global Recruiter and Talent Manager",
                    "employment_type": null
                }
            ]
